{"tid":1333953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721一定要諗定對付鄉黑方法！！","createTime":"2019-07-20T02:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:03:50.000Z","uid":38991,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a9415ec8bbae92d1bf4e8af4710a52b6c27a75","tid":1333953,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"預左有人會黎攪事撩交打<br />\n然後黑警出黎收割人頭<br />\n但係經過沙田一戰<br />\n平民裝既鄉黑又有咩好怕wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.被人挑釁要保持冷靜，不主動攻擊<br />\n黑警就係想你打，佢就合理拉你，同時在場好多記者影住，唔好比任何機會黑警扭轉形象<br />\n<br />\n2.被人打一定要還手<br />\n被人打先就係自衛，有還手既正當性，我地人多，只要敢還手班鄉黑一定驚過你，到時成班仲唔收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6180d6a37dfc67fb9f56c6906349a3a0b1b7b859","tid":1333953,"uid":275331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"全民帶索帶，制伏佢"},{"pid":"ae6581114a7fddd66104f5a9b4d3b37090a47c4a","tid":1333953,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n<br />\n大叫便衣警殺人"},{"pid":"d5ba678c874fa8c1f308af29cdaddaffd8ce8e38","tid":1333953,"uid":148332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"打要打得聰明同有決心，唔好同佢地長時間高聲對罵，咁會引左d差佬埋黎。<br />\n要打就直接開波，圍上去1分鐘已經夠收佢皮，然後化整為零繼續行"},{"pid":"98320c9a879ae2b6d1c121bb31092866d5d5f6ca","tid":1333953,"uid":12171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"721差佬係水馬內龜縮，自己人開遮之後就做乜都唔怕啦<br />\n<br />\n可以參考尋晚新城市隻休班警俾人圍，最後要靠救護車先走到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19519c809760b8ec2687a382f349f12410ebc612","tid":1333953,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"一係就唔好理佢由佢嘈 警察嚟到見到得佢發癲<br />\n（不過唔排除警方選擇性做野 大家唔打佢唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n一係就一秒十幾人圍住佢 用索帶索佢手手腳腳<br />\n之後就散開<br />\n（希望大家有默契啲 同有吉士啲 齊圍齊索齊散）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日 721見！！！"},{"pid":"b001583c82068baf5e2cf1507ab7439be1495194","tid":1333953,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d1220436fee3e35ccb3c59cc40e4a01edc28aa03","tid":1333953,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"一定要還手"},{"pid":"20e2c4cdcd7f10919557e4baa2be62f655af9ffa","tid":1333953,"uid":269179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"開遮，就還手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c84eceac29e565d2aacdef7100ffcd223c6214","tid":1333953,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"用愛感化佢"},{"pid":"4ef67e96184c596f8c6b85d569b500ef96549165","tid":1333953,"uid":8465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"索帶制服完之後圍住示眾。"},{"pid":"4d31b01fad4e89bab6f4ff33a2c1a1aa98636ada","tid":1333953,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"唔好人踩人啊"},{"pid":"778fc7bfc8884c0cb873e59d3b4f29463866526f","tid":1333953,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"982bfed75b293b33de0a070f65567a3a73e59029","tid":1333953,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔好俾機會D 警察 sip D人入去"},{"pid":"f97fe07c0dd56568f8918e8b34a5a42bbfe85525","tid":1333953,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"